text: Abduwali Muse (born 1990) is a Somali pirate. In 2009, he captured a ship from the United States and took its captain Richard Phillips as hostage. He was sentenced to over 33 years in prison on 16 February 2011. ==References== Category:Somali people Category:Pirates Category:1990 births Category:Living people
